Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a SLAM-based mobile laser scanning solution for mapping indoor environments. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper involves point cloud processing, wall plane detection, and semantic labeling. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are possible categories as the paper may involve machine learning or AI techniques for semantic labeling. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category, but it could be relevant as the paper may involve visualization of the furniture-free maps.
